    {
      "id": "33",
      "name": "画廊",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "gallery_character",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/10/27/36540823/d1bb7ec9ceccf9758053aa0ed34fbf09_6222311366179910187.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>旅行者使用并召出「尘歌壶」后，可以与「尘歌壶」交互进入「尘歌壶」内。</p><p>当旅行者处于「尘歌壶」内时，也可以使用并召出「尘歌壶」，与「尘歌壶」交互后，即可离开「尘歌壶」。</p><p>旅行者还可以直接打开地图界面，使用传送锚点进行传送，直接离开「尘歌壶」。</p>",
                "key": "尘歌壶 1"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/10/27/36540823/97b4b55c929db9eaf9ef438f8f18b3b4_7573774332398960008.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>在<span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">「尘歌壶」</span>内，可以在<span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">壶灵</span>处了解和操作<span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">「尘歌壶」</span>的诸项事宜。</p>",
                "key": "尘歌壶 2"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/10/27/36540823/326e4ddae739da5c55e3d132309ef581_5678853164354097466.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>通过制作界面，可以制作各种物品。</p>",
                "key": "尘歌壶 3"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/10/27/36540823/6248324f6b8057557d6871ea32c23c4b_8992757374460603117.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>可以在世界各处搜集制作物品所需的材料。</p>",
                "key": "尘歌壶 4"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/10/27/36540823/f016c4cb1effb82035cf9d8a0b9e222d_5463767432933868309.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>在获得了摆设后，可以通过放置功能对其进行摆设。</p>",
                "key": "尘歌壶 5"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/10/27/36540823/ac58638274c6b8b29d8a06191cf98071_842840757190034186.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>成功放置摆设，可以提升尘歌壶的<span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">洞天仙力等阶</span>。随着仙力等阶的提高，洞天宝钱的搜聚速度也会随之增加。</p>",
                "key": "尘歌壶 6"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/10/27/36540823/b6e632172830fcb550fc2391b99f0d4e_2994837334037440725.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">洞天宝钱</span>可以在<span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">洞天百宝</span>内交换各种物品。</p>",
                "key": "尘歌壶 7"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/10/27/36540823/8a14725abeeba03dc5faed31fa057655_2311463602979922510.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>每隔一段时间，都会有一位周游壶灵造访洞天。这位周游壶灵，也许会带有一些珍稀的货。</p>",
                "key": "尘歌壶 8"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/10/27/36540823/2237ab5a1d18dd3ee5490d5b5b1bfd10_3282115082900242442.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>如果获得了摆设装图纸，就可以进行对许多摆设进行批量放置。放置时，单间摆设依然可以进行微调。</p>",
                "key": "尘歌壶 9"
              }
            ],
            "pic": ""
          }
        }
      ]
    },
